{"type":null,"faqId":49541,"title":"开启或关闭飞行模式","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.3784722in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"飞行模式\"XE \"航空模式\"XE \"离线模式\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>背景信息</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189896\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n <span>手机信号的接收或发射会干扰飞机上的电子设备和通讯，影响飞行安全。在乘坐飞机时，请按照工作人员的要求开启飞行模式或关机。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n <span>开启飞行模式后，手机将无法使用网络和通讯功能，但是您仍然可以使用手机中的本地娱乐功能，比如音乐播放器、游戏等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>任务示例</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以通过以下几种方式开启或关闭“飞行模式”：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n <span>从状态栏处向下滑动，打开通知面板。在“开关”页签下，点击“飞行模式”开关，开启或关闭飞行模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n <span>长按电源键，然后点击“飞行模式”，开启或关闭飞行模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n <span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189897\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”，然后切换到“全部设置”页签。在“无线和网络”区域，点击“更多”，然后点击“飞行模式”开关，开启或关闭飞行模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>开启飞行模式后，状态栏中会显示飞行模式图标“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189898\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5285","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294508000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":26,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}